  <title>GlobeControlOpenGLDrawing</title>
  <purpose><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">This sample demonstrates how to draw within GlobeControl using the OpenGL library. The sample has two sections, one command and one tool. The command demonstrates how to draw a geographical point on the globe while the tool demonstrates how to convert and draw a window coordinate on the globe. </div></purpose>
